# Git commits

- After completing a batch of code or config changes, stage the changed files and commit automatically (unless the user has asked not to, or the repo is not the current workspace).
- Every commit message must start with `[Cursor]` (e.g. `[Cursor] fix: correct date formatting` or `[Cursor] feat(auth): add login endpoint`).
